features: MINIMALIST DESIGN: MFASCO's first aid kit box showcases a clean, white finish with no first aid markings or labels, perfect for maintaining a professional and uncluttered workspace. This metal cabinet blends seamlessly into any office or shop decor.

HIGH STANDARDS OF SAFETY: MFASCO’s first aid kit is ANSI Z308.1-2021 Class B compliant, and is ideal for OSHA compliance, ensuring a professional level of workplace safety. This commitment to rigorous regulations makes it an ideal first aid kit for businesses and a reliable part of any emergency medical kit.

ORGANIZED ACCESSIBILITY: All products within this first aid kit box are thoughtfully packed in dispensing boxes for easy access. Each box is clearly labeled for quick identification of contents during critical moments. This shop first aid kit is designed for efficiency and convenience.

PREMIUM QUALITY PRODUCTS: This workplace first aid kit comes equipped with the highly reputed Medifirst brand of bandages and medications. The premium quality of these items ensures that your office first aid kit is ready to handle any emergency situations efficiently.

SPACIOUS STORAGE: This workplace medical kit features four shelves of products and a door pouch for smaller items, all neatly housed within a robust metal cabinet. It's the perfect balance of compact size and ample storage, with dimensions measuring 15 x 21 x 5 1/2 inches.
body.description: The MFASCO first aid kit box features a minimalist design with a sleek white finish, making it an ideal fit for any professional environment. Adhering to ANSI and OSHA standards, it promises a high level of safety, making it an indispensable part of any workplace's emergency medical supplies. For ease of use, the kit is organized with all items packed in labeled dispensing boxes, ensuring quick accessibility during emergencies. The kit includes premium Medifirst brand bandages and medications, guaranteeing readiness to efficiently handle any emergency. The robust metal cabinet comprises four shelves and a door pouch for smaller items, neatly organizing the supplies in a compact space measuring 15 x 21 x 5 1/2 inches.
